reviewText: Excellent quality and great price. All set to use in U.S. DVD players. Definitely a good buy.

My grandson(Maison) loved it.  He is a huge fan of the Pingu collection. I hope to make sure he has the entire collection. Its one of those DVD(s) that has him laughing out loud. and watching it for hours. Even though they don't speak our language. Masion seems to be able to follow the story line.
